org.kocakosm.pitaya.collection

Interface Bag<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of the elements in the bag.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Collection<E>, Iterable<E>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ConcurrentBag<E>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractBag, ArrayBag, ConcurrentHashBag, CopyOnWriteArrayBag, HashBag, ImmutableBag

    public interface Bag<E>
extends Collection<E>
    A collection that supports order-independent equality, like Set, but, which may have duplicate elements.
    Author:
    Osman KOCAK
    See Also:
    Collection, AbstractBag, ArrayBag, HashBag, ConcurrentHashBag, CopyOnWriteArrayBag, ImmutableBag, Bags
